  <oversight_info>
    <has_dmc>No</has_dmc>
  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this observational epidemiological study is to investigate the management and
      the complications associated with severe trauma. Data will be analysed to answer pre-defined
      scientific projects and to improve management of these conditions.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Anonymous data will be collected by study coordinators in a secured e-database. Cross audit
      will be performed to check data.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
