    </study_pop>
    <sampling_method>Non-Probability Sample</sampling_method>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  severe trauma

          -  and/or traumatic brain injury

          -  and/or hemorrhage

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Consent withdrawal
